OL,3,CTenants of city's oldest allotment
OL,4,Cordered off plots
OL,6,FThe tenants of Bath's oldest allotment
OL,7,Fhave been ordered to leave their plots
OL,8,Fafter the site's landowner cut ties
OL,9,Fwith the council.
OL,11,FCombe Down Allotment has been in
OL,12,Faction for 130 years, but 64 allotment
OL,13,Fholders are now being served a notice
OL,14,Fto leave by October 2025.
OL,16,FBath & North East Somerset Council
OL,17,Fleases the site, but has been told it
OL,18,Fmust quit the land.
