OL,6,FCampaign group Save Combe Down
OL,7,FAllotments has made national headlines
OL,8,Fin its fight to save the site.
OL,10,FIn a Facebook statement following the
OL,11,Feviction news, it said: "And it's
OL,12,Fofficial, we have been served notice
OL,13,Fand have one more growing season left
OL,14,Funtil we have to leave so let's make
OL,15,Fthe most of it!
