OL,6,F"We will not give up hope that
OL,7,Fsomething can be done to save this
OL,8,Fhistoric allotment site. We have no
OL,9,Fidea what the landowner is planning to
OL,10,Fdo with the site if nothing can be
OL,11,Fdone to prevent the eviction
OL,12,Fhappening."
OL,14,FBath & North East Somerset Council has
OL,15,Fsaid it's still working on
OL,16,Fnegotiations with the landowner, in
OL,17,Fthe hope of buying the site - but all
OL,18,Frequests for a meeting have been
OL,19,Fdeclined by his solicitor.
