OL,3,CTenants of city's oldest allotment
OL,4,Cordered off plots
OL,6,FCouncillor Tim Ball, cabinet member
OL,7,Ffor neighbourhoods, said: "We are
OL,8,Fextremely disappointed to have to send
OL,9,Fa notice to quit to our allotment
OL,10,Fholders.
OL,12,F"This is not the outcome the council
OL,13,Fdesires. Our preferred option is the
OL,14,Fpurchase of the site which we will
OL,15,Fcontinue to work towards in our
OL,16,Fnegotiations with the landowner."
