OL,6,FLetters to allotment holders say the
OL,7,Fcouncil's interest in the allotment
OL,8,Fsite in the absence of any other
OL,9,Fcircumstances prevailing will come to
OL,10,Fan end on November 30, 2025.
OL,12,FAllotment holders are being asked to
OL,13,Fleave their plots by October 31, 2025,
OL,14,Fto allow enough time for the council
OL,15,Fto reinstate the land as required by
OL,16,Fthe terms of its own lease.
OL,18,FEarlier this year the council wrote to
OL,19,Fallotment holders setting out the
OL,20,Fcomplex legal situation and its
OL,21,Fcommitment to remain on the site.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
