OL,6,FIt's since added the allotment to its
OL,7,Flist of Assets of Community Value
OL,8,Fbecause of campaigning from Save Combe
OL,9,FDown Allotments - this gives the
OL,10,Fcouncil greater power in its bid to
OL,11,Fbuy the site.
OL,13,FThe landowner has previously been
OL,14,Fcontacted for a response but said they
OL,15,Fhad no comment to make.
